Add Widgets to the Dashboard

A date filter widget allows dashboard viewers to filter the CRM Analytics dashboard results based on a selected date range.

Drag the date widget to the dashboard canvas. Click the button inside the widget to open the wizard. Select the date field that you want to filter on and click Create.

Behind the scenes, CRM Analytics creates a query grouped by the field that you selected. The widget doesn't apply any selections to it, by default.

To change the widget properties, select the widget in the dashboard canvas. Specify whether to show absolute, relative, or preset dates, select the default calendar type and use a List of presets for a fixed interval.

Select applicable intervals and click Save to save the changes to the dashboard.
